name: TableSelectionBehavior
description: Selection behavior of the `ui5-table` selection components.

values.name: RowSelector
values.description: Rows can only be selected by using the row selector column.
values._jsDoc:
/**
 * Rows can only be selected by using the row selector column.
 * 
 * @private
 */

values.name: RowOnly
values.description:
Rows can only be selected by clicking directly on the row, as the row selector column is hidden.

**Note:** In this mode, the `row-click` event of the `ui5-table` component is not fired.
